cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with video-based action recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed technique involves using deep features and a non-linear knowledge transfer model, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions using Fourier Temporal Pyramid, which is a technique commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and signal processing (cs.NE).
